node.text: HAPPY ANNIVERSARY, ERNESTINE. Here are my two girls yesterday, Ernestine and Hazel. Ernestine won’t love me posting because she’s without makeup. She still looks pretty great to me. I love you, Ernestine.

node.text: Ahhhh, golf in Palm Springs. Give me 110 degrees and an empty course and I’m a a happy guy.
